    "human-animal interaction and ethical responsibilities is key to ensuring the welfare of farm animals while supporting sustainable agricultural practices.",
    "By aligning technological advancements with animal-centered farming and promoting collaboration between stakeholders, HACI technologies have the potential to advance both animal welfare and operational efficiency, meeting the growing consumer demand for ethically produced food.",
